<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title> 프로필 업로드 성공! </title>
  <style>
    html {
      background-color: black;
    }

    .profile {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 100px;
      color: white;
    }

    .box {
      width: 200px;
      height: 250px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="profile">
    <div class="box">
      <img class="img" src="/<%= src %>" alt="">
    </div>
    <h4> <%= id %> 님, 환영합니다! </h4>
  </div>
</body>

</html>